  net worth  million spouses gregg couch children  website httpswwwapplecomprbiosangelaahrendtshtml angela jean ahrendts dbe born june   is an american businesswoman and the senior vice president of retail at apple inc she was the ceo of burberry from  to  ahrendts left burberry to join apple in  ahrendts was ranked th in forbes  list of the most powerful women in the world th most powerful woman in the uk in the bbc radio  woman’s hour  power list and th in fortune’s  list of the worlds most powerful women in business she was also a member of the uks prime ministers business advisory council until it was disbanded in  contents  early life  career  burberry  apple  awards and memberships  personal life  references  external links early lifeedit ahrendts was born and raised in new palestine indiana the third of six children her father richard ahrendts was a businessman and her mother jean was a homemaker she attended new palestine high school where she was a varsity cheerleader in  she earned an undergraduate degree in merchandising and marketing from ball state university in muncie indiana in  she received an honorary doctorate of humane letters from ball state careeredit ahrendts moved to new york city to work in the fashion industry after a series of positions including merchandising at bra maker warnaco ahrendts joined donna karan international in  working to develop the luxury brand internationally through both wholesale and licensing in  she was hired at henri bendel by leslie wexner to expand bendel stores to  new markets but the project was cancelled by the board of directors two years later in  she joined fifth  pacific companies as vice president of corporate merchandising and design in  she was promoted to senior vice president corporate merchandising and group president responsible for the merchandising of the groups  plus brands including laundry by shelli segal lucky brand dungarees and the mens retail business of liz claiborne inc in  she was promoted again to serve as executive vice president with full responsibility for the complete line of liz claiborne products services and development across both womens and mens lines burberryedit ahrendts joined burberry in january  and took up the position of ceo on july   replacing rose marie bravo ahrendts mitigated the brands decline in prestige by immediately limiting the number of clothing and accessories carrying the burberry check pattern to  minimizing the damage ubiquitous counterfeits had caused to sales she also oversaw the buying out of the spanish franchise which was then generating  of group revenues to stop its unfettered licensing ahrendts says she did not model her approach after any other fashion house but looked to worldclass design as an influence including apple inc the company value rose during her tenure from £ billion to over £ billion cnn money reported that during  she was the highest paid ceo in the uk making  million appleedit on october   it was announced that ahrendts would leave burberry in spring  to join apple inc as a member of its executive team as senior vice president of retail and online stores filling the spot vacated by john browett in october  on may   apples new svp of retail and online stores angela ahrendts was placed on the apple leadership roster signaling her official entry into the company according to apples  proxy statement filed with the securities and exchange commission ahrendts earned over  million in  more than any other executive at apple including ceo tim cook as of august  she is reported to own approximately us million worth of apple shares she is the only female senior executive at apple awards and membershipsedit  crain’s new york rising stars  under  –present prime minister’s business advisory group member  cnbc european business leader of the future  oracle world retail awards outstanding leadership award  st george’s society of new york medal of honor  also  financial times top  women in world business  shenkar college of engineering and design honorary fellow  business of fashion bof   the most excellent order of the british empire a dbe for services to british business  also   fortune’s businesspeople of the year     ranked  in fortunes  top people in business  financial times women of   also       forbes’  most powerful women in the world  th most powerful woman in the united kingdom by womans hour on bbc radio   fast company most creative people in business  also      fortune’s  most powerful women in business personal lifeedit ahrendts met her husband gregg couch in elementary school they married in their s after a year longdistance relationship the couple has three children when ahrendts was working at burberry the family lived in a  square feet  m home on an  acres  ha plot west of london brought up a methodist she is still an active christian referencesedit  httpwwwsalarycomangelaahrendtssalarybonusstockoptionsforappleinchtml  a b c d e f g h i j hass nancy  september  earning her stripes the wall street journal archived from the original on  september    a ahrendts  united states public records familysearch retrieved  january    angela ahrendts businessweek retrieved  february    fried ina  october  apple hires burberry ceo angela ahrendts to head its retail efforts all things digital retrieved  october    howard caroline the worlds most powerful women  forbes forbescom llc retrieved  june    a b the power list  bbc radio  womans hour   fairchild caroline leahey colleen vandermey ane  the most powerful women in business fortune retrieved  september    httpswwwgovukgovernmentnewsbusinessadvisorygroup  theresa may tells big business advisers no more advice please the guardian sept  a b chu jeff  january  can apples angela ahrendts spark a retail revolution fast company retrieved  october    barnett maxwell  october  hoosier angela ahrendts leaves burberry for apple indianapolis monthly retrieved  october    a b executive profile  angela ahrendts businessweek  retr