moted again to serve as executive vice president with full responsibility for the complete line of liz claiborne products services and development across both womens and mens lines burberryedit ahrendts joined burberry in january  and took up the position of ceo on july   replacing rose marie bravo ahrendts mitigated the brands decline in prestige by immediately limiting the number of clothing and accessories carrying the burberry check pattern to  minimizing the damage ubiquitous counterfeits had caused to sales she also oversaw the buying out of the spanish franchise which was then generating  of group revenues to stop its unfettered licensing ahrendts says she did not model her approach after any other fashion house but looked to worldclass design as an influence including apple inc the company value rose during her tenure from £ billion to over £ billion cnn money reported that during  she was the highest paid ceo in the uk making  million appleedit on october   it was announced that ahrendts would leave burberry in spring  to join apple inc as a member of its executive team as senior vice president of retail and online stores filling the spot vacated by john browett in october  on may   apples new svp of retail and online stores angela ahrendts was placed on the apple leadership roster signaling her official entry into the company according to apples  proxy statement filed with the securities and exchange commission ahrendts earned over  million in  more than any other executive at apple including ceo tim cook as of august  she is reported to own approximately us million worth of apple shares she is the only female senior executive at apple awards and membershipsedit  crain’s new york rising stars  under  –present prime minister’s business advisory group member  cnbc european business leader of the future  oracle world retail awards outstanding leadership award  st george’s society of new york medal of honor  also  financial times top  women in world business  