ng im guilty of always being incredibly focused on the task at hand so wherever ive worked ive just always tried to do my best achieve my best build a great team around me angela ahrendts team best great i am not in favour of quotas just put the best person into the job it is not about gender it is about experience leadership and vision angela ahrendts leadership best experience in china youve got six people buying for one child but the thing is youve got the largest rising uppermiddle class in the world angela ahrendts world child people forget luxury as a great company you have to keep evolving angela ahrendts great luxury you it is one of the most important parts of my job showing that you cant do it all angela ahrendts job important you i dont want to be a great chief executive without being a great mum and a great wife angela ahrendts great wife want i hadnt grown up always aspiring to be a ceo angela ahrendts up ceo always youre going to see relationships with technology across anything thats brand i dont care if thats in home or what you wear i just think its a new fact of life angela ahrendts life home technology just because youre a luxury brand doesnt mean you have to have an attitude angela ahrendts attitude brand luxury store windows are like landing pages on the website angela ahrendts windows website landing share this page cite this page citation find on amazon angela ahrendts related authors mary kay ash sheryl sandberg barbara corcoran marissa mayer carly fiorina margaret heffernan anne m mulcahy katharine graham brainyquote desktop brainyquote mobile site home authors topics quote of the day pictures top  quotes professions birthdays social bq on facebook bq on twitter bq on pinterest bq on google bq on instagram shop brainyquote store apps iphoneipad app quote of the day feeds javascript and rss feeds wordpress plugin quote of the day email about about us contact us submit privacy terms copyright     brainyquote language español  français   loadin